{"tid":688220,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"「經濟型美食天堂」中國既酸奶，海底撈， 麻辣，喜茶，打邊爐","createTime":"2018-06-03T04:35:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-03T05:41:57.000Z","uid":123335,"like":18,"dislike":55,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fa7af82f64e7a883d03eccb3856dd620e167c609","tid":688220,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T04:35:01.000Z","msg":"中國真係好多好野食 <br />\n酸奶，海底撈， 麻辣，喜茶，打邊爐<br />\n每樣美食都獨當一面 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n價錢經濟到不得了 <br />\n食過一次真係上晒癮<br />\n返唔到轉頭 <br />\n<br />\n香港d 野太貴啦今時今日<br />\noverpriced  晒<br />\n<br />\n得罪講句<br />\n香港食野 =  俾錢食鋪租"},{"pid":"fb3dc228b9807dc9a60d46ebba8c7cfca3cdfb5e","tid":688220,"uid":123335,"like":9,"dislike":14,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T04:37:28.000Z","msg":"香港要食好野唔係唔得 <br />\n但真心好撚貴 <br />\n你用平民價得d 垃圾俾你食 <br />\n用同樣價錢真係寧願上大陸食<br />\n<br />\n因為呢d 平價餐廳d 來貨咪又係大陸<br />\n你以為好安全咩<br />\n<br />\n老實講<br />\n用同樣既價錢<br />\n真係上大陸食抵屌好多"},{"pid":"5efbee4a974b63e012f731feb719b5437dc4cd1f","tid":688220,"uid":123335,"like":5,"dislike":13,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T04:39:59.000Z","msg":"我知你地實話我中國5毛<br />\n大佬呀<br />\n窮係咁架啦 <br />\n食唔起香港d 米芝連123星呀屌 <br />\n食唔起香港d 師傅發辦呀屌"},{"pid":"28e2469aef68ef969b8a34fb750cbaeca999cf8b","tid":688220,"uid":47139,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T04:45:21.000Z","msg":"樓主rip"},{"pid":"8b848d01e76cea78de72a9adf92b907efb66e9d4","tid":688220,"uid":123335,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"28e2469aef68ef969b8a34fb750cbaeca999cf8b","tid":688220,"uid":47139,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T04:45:21.000Z","msg":"樓主rip"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T04:47:04.000Z","msg":"都唔知大家驚咩<br />\n人地非洲d 人又伊波拉 ，食水又有寄生蟲<br />\n日子咪又係咁過<br />\n<br />\n食元素週期表呢d 其實好濕醉"},{"pid":"af60bb36bde15fed7b0ce6a4108aac2b048fd2b7","tid":688220,"uid":61832,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-03T04:47:47.000Z",